-- Islamists in U.A.E Had Links With ‘External Elements’: WAM
-- B y   Z a i d   S a b a h
-- 2012-08-13T01:44:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-13/islamists-in-u-a-e-had-links-with-external-elements-wam.html
The Islamists arrested in the  United
Arab Emirates  for conspiring against the state had links with
“external elements” and had worked in an “organized” manner,
the state-run news agency  WAM  reported, citing a statement by
the cabinet.  The individuals were causing harm to the country and
spreading false information to incite others, according to the
statement, the news agency said, without elaborating.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zaid Sabah Abd Alhamid in Washington at 
 zalhamid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
